### User API 테스트

### 내 정보 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me
Content-Type: application/json

### 내 정보 수정
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "홍길동",
  "profileImageUrl": "https://example.com/profile.jpg"
}

### 회원 탈퇴
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me
Content-Type: application/json
